{"tid":1240501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：仍有很多工作想做　未來三年將非常忙碌","createTime":"2019-06-18T11:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T11:30:27.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"55365f0e2694209fe8725abdec29bb26c9f2080e","tid":1240501,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1463615_1_L_20190618165951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1463615_1_L_20190618165951.jpg&h=fd13e4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥在記者會上表示，留意到坊間對她過去數日與不同團體的閉門會議有很多說法，最重要是她今日嚴肅、真誠地向市民致歉，認為這是作為行政長官應該負的最大責任。<br />\n<br />\n她又稱，經過今次事件，未來3年將會非常困難，但特區政府團隊有信心，會加倍努力，重新獲得市民的信心。"},{"pid":"ca4197d860f959161a830ae30a8788845162e69a","tid":1240501,"uid":32577,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:06:27.000Z","msg":"明日大愚 國歌法 23條 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24162ce415b43a8ac1a4d0c6b358af5f94e52c2","tid":1240501,"uid":168716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:06:44.000Z","msg":"like I care what u want to do next <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n777真係無改錯名"},{"pid":"e3f5768124092fa46729f3db4d9511e0561038f7","tid":1240501,"uid":245409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:08:26.000Z","msg":"你老母仲忙碌"},{"pid":"b98fe9468b2fdeab6bb4c3426528f3a6a4dfe0d6","tid":1240501,"uid":87979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"個樣勁不㞕"},{"pid":"1919ecffe82ee9669a894c987996a3cccd9e31d8","tid":1240501,"uid":12824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca4197d860f959161a830ae30a8788845162e69a","tid":1240501,"uid":32577,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:06:27.000Z","msg":"明日大愚 國歌